This paper is primarily focused on machine learning and optimization techniques for recurrent neural networks (RNNs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of RNNs in natural language processing (NLP) tasks, which suggests a possible connection to cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper's focus on online learning and control suggests a possible connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
